{"prompt": "Generate a website for a real estate brokerage. The website should be modern and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Premier Properties</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            background-color: #e6f0ff;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #0056b3;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #003d80;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #e6f0ff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            color: #007bff;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: #555;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .properties-section, .contact-section {\n            background-color: white;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .properties-section h2, .contact-section h2 {\n            color: #007bff;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n        .property-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        .property-card {\n            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        .property-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .property-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n        .property-info {\n            padding: 15px;\n        }\n        .property-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #007bff;\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n        }\n        .property-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #666;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        .property-info .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: #28a745;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .contact-section form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        .contact-section input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-section input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-section textarea {\n            width: 80%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        .contact-section textarea {\n            min-height: 120px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        .contact-section button {\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-section button:hover {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: white;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Premier Properties</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#properties\">Properties</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"hero\">\n            <h2>Your Dream Home Awaits</h2>\n            <p>Discover exceptional homes and unparalleled service with Premier Properties. We connect you with the perfect place to live.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"properties\" class=\"properties-section\">\n            <h2>Featured Properties</h2>\n            <div class=\"property-grid\">\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/007bff/ffffff?text=Luxury+Condo\" alt=\"Luxury Condo\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Modern City Condo</h3>\n                        <p>Stunning 2-bedroom condo with city views and premium amenities.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$650,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/007bff/ffffff?text=Family+Home\" alt=\"Family Home\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Spacious Family Home</h3>\n                        <p>Charming 4-bedroom home in a quiet, family-friendly neighborhood.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$475,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/007bff/ffffff?text=Waterfront+Villa\" alt=\"Waterfront Villa\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Seaside Villa</h3>\n                        <p>Elegant 3-bedroom villa with breathtaking oceanfront access.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$1,200,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/007bff/ffffff?text=Downtown+Loft\" alt=\"Downtown Loft\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Chic Downtown Loft</h3>\n                        <p>Stylish 1-bedroom loft with industrial-chic design in the heart of the city.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$390,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-section\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Premier Properties. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add smooth scrolling for navigation links\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}